{"tid":2444583,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"港台：中美下周會談　選址阿拉斯加別具意義","createTime":"2021-03-13T02:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T04:20:59.000Z","uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2b4048f1f5213d54703ce72ccc0e5c529ca6c1d3","tid":2444583,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T02:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中美高層官員將於下星期在美國阿拉斯加進行2+2會面，是美國總統拜登上任以來，中美高層首次面對面會談。外界關注兩國在貿易、人權、南海、台灣以至香港等議題上，能取得多大程度上的成果。<br />\n<br />\n有分析認為，今次會議的選址定於阿拉斯加是精心謹慎，認為阿拉斯加遠離美國本土，帶有中立意義，<strong>亦反映中方對外顯示出不願對美方作出過多讓步的姿態。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580373-20210313.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580373-20210313.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXI8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=d1a9a305\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580373-20210313.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0fd365bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580373-20210313.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"79425334115d30b02eddfdf4590fd162f09b5b8d","tid":2444583,"uid":58630,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T02:36:29.000Z","msg":"上次夏威夷唔係仲遠過阿拉斯加咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁都有得打飛機<br />\n不如下次上太空搞"},{"pid":"33ca6064bc00ee53ab8464ecd10280579fd8de7f","tid":2444583,"uid":103050,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T02:39:26.000Z","msg":"美國揀得阿拉斯加都幾明顯唔係咩友善姿態<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a771852363a0358d10bc5d390478a0f75c5c271b","tid":2444583,"uid":288913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"33ca6064bc00ee53ab8464ecd10280579fd8de7f","ti